channel.title: A couple of my new models
channel.description:
Been bored for a couple weeks, had a lot of time on my hands so I decided to make these:
Dragon Claws: [IMG]http://i453.photobucket.com/albums/qq251/RuneModelMaker/DragonClaws.jpg[/img] This one I made an arm brace then placed it, next I resized my D War Scimmy and made small blades with it. Therefore making claws.
Gun Blade: [IMG]http://i453.photobucket.com/albums/qq251/RuneModelMaker/GunBlade.jpg[/img] Last time I made it looked 2d, so I decided to make it again but more 3d.
Masamune: [IMG]http://i453.photobucket.com/albums/qq251/RuneModelMaker/Masamune-1.jpg[/img] An updated version of my last Masamune, made it look more like the real one from FF7.
Skill Cape Template: [IMG]http://i453.photobucket.com/albums/qq251/RuneModelMaker/SkillCapeTemplate.jpg[/img] The many different colors are to help noobs know what color they want to change, all mats are named.
Sword Template: [IMG]http://i453.photobucket.com/albums/qq251/RuneModelMaker/SwordTemplate.jpg[/img] This is a small sword I made so that noobs could edit it to their liking and start off their modeling career.
Taif Dagger: [IMG]http://i453.photobucket.com/albums/qq251/RuneModelMaker/TaifDagger.jpg[/img] I made this about 3 months ago but it looked terrible so I fixed glitching, lengthened blade, and made handle smaller.
What do you people think?
